specific_question: What was our compliance audit cost as a percentage of annual revenue in Q3 2025?
answer: Compliance audit cost was 1.5% of annual revenue with a total cost of $4.5 million.
justification: Compliance audit costs do not address the optimization of quality assurance processes for electric vehicle production
